            <h3>ARTWORK SUBMISSIONS</h3>
            <p>              Artwork Templates<br />
              Buyer may request www.BoostPromotions.com to email an adobe  Photoshop layered template once an order has been completed online. <br />
              <br />
              File Types<br />
              Buyer may submit artwork in the following formats:&nbsp;jpg,  tiff, pdf, psd, ai. All images mst be 300 dpi for offset print  quality.&nbsp;Artwork must be submitted or constructed as a CMYK file. <br />
              <br />
              Fonts<br />
            If Buyer provides layered files, they must also provide the  fonts used in the creation of the files. Failure to do so may result in a substituded font that is not the same as Buyers submission. </p>
<p>              Font Sizes<br />
              &nbsp;Artwork should not have fonts smaller than 8  point for legibility and clear printing without ghosting. Avoid using drop  shadows or other layer effects on text that is smaller than 10 points. <br />
              <br />
              Die Cutting&nbsp;Designs submitted for printing that will be  DIE CUT must have a bleed area of 1/8&rdquo; beyond the cut line. Design should avoid  straight edges that are within Â¼&ldquo; of die cut edges. Die cutting will vary by as  much as 1/16&rdquo; from side to side. Design should not have any printing within  1/8&rdquo; of any die cut edge. <br />
              <br />
              Color Matching<br />
              Online images, Email images, Inkjet prints, Laser prints and  digital proofs are not adequate for color matching print work. Each computer  screen may vary substantially from another as a result of individual  calibration and settings. <br />
              <br />
              If color matching is required, Buyer will need to mail  actual samples of&nbsp;artwork to www.BoostPromotions.com and specify in  writing the desired PANTONE color numbers. <br />
              <br />
            A Pantone color guide swatch book may be ordered at 800 892  8805.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Orders that involve color matching are not able to be run or ganged up with other orders which results in additional expense and additional time to complete the order.  For additional questions about color matching, please contact us at 909 231 5837</p>
<p>              If Buyer is ordering multiple products or different kinds of  products it must be understood that the printing process is different from one  medium to another and color may not be the same from one fabric to another or  from plastic to paper etc.&nbsp;www.BoostPromotions.com cannot guarantee color  matching between one product to another  for branded product orders. <br />
